snippet.title: Barbie: Beauty Boutique
snippet.description: Gameplay of Barbie beauty boutique. Some parts were cut out due to older XP/98 games not working with fraps. I also apologize for the sound. I had to use my mic since I wasn't able to record the system sounds.
